belongs_to_collection.name: Corbin Fisher's All American Workouts Series

overview: Every muscle gets a workout in Corbin Fisher's gym. Beau works out Wesley, Calan and Hugh get it on in the gym, Elian and Casey pump some muscle, and Evan and Dave work up a sweat in this full-length, fourth installment of CF's All American Workouts series. The hottest American college men pump more than iron in All American Workouts Vol. 4.
title: All American Workouts 4
